episodes.title: S1 E13 - Religion and Spirituality - Cults
episodes.description: Tune in to this thought-provoking episode about a cult hidden in plain sight within a sleepy suburban neighborhood in Austin, TX. Cult survivor and published author, Julia Heart, shares her harrowing experience as a devoted cult member. Learn how she found freedom from the mental chains that held her captive and went on to live a fulfilling life. Subscribe, Follow, Like - you know - all the things! Thank you!  #cults #cultsurvivors #cultredflags #yellowrose #sextrafficking #sexualtrauma
